column4:
Jesu, Mestowot, i-ndoi-ywech;
Ribech eng' euneguk.
Ki cheguget; nyo iyumech;
Egu Kando-indennyo.
Jesu Kristo, iberurech;
Ki-i-alech; ki cheguk.
Jesu Kristo, iberurech;
Ki-i-alech; ki cheguk.

Ki-imwa ile itaa-chech
Nganda ki muruonen  kot.
Soruech, Jesu , eng' chamyengung ,
Ak itililech iman.
Jesu Kristo , iberurech;
Namech eng' euneguk.
Jesu Kristo , iberurech ;
Namech eng' euneguk.

Toretech keyai mage-ng'ung`
Eng' betusiekyok tugul.
Inyiitech  Tamirmirieng'ung;
Ba-enech Ng'olyondeng'ung'
Jesu Kristo, iberurech;
Ak igaswech saennyo.
Jesu Kristo, iberurech;
Ak igaswech saennyo.

Kichamech Jesu, kinyo koyetech, 
Kinyo komechech achek tugul. 

CHORUS
Kichamech Yetindet; machei koyetech; 
Machei komutech gab Jehovah. 

Wechech bunyondet, masambwanindet; 
Machei komutech oldab oik. 

Ya koret ne bo masambwanindet; 
Arogendos kot oik tugul. 

Kigoyok Kwanda Werinnyi Jesu; 
Kinyo konetech ng'alek che Miach. 

Machei komutech kebe orennyi; 
Machei kobaiba-it chi tugul.
